lo Bilbao]]|ESP}}\n|{{Ct|AST|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| + 11' 50\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 7\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Patrick Konrad]]|AUT}}\n|{{Ct|BOH|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| + 13' 01\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 8\n|{{Flagathlete|[[George Bennett (cyclist)|George Bennett]]|NZL}}\n|{{Ct|TLJ|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| + 13' 17\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 9\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Sam Oomen]]|NED}}\n|{{Ct|SUN|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| + 14' 18\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 10\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Davide Formolo]]|ITA}}\n|{{Ct|BOH|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| + 15' 16\"\n|}\n\n{{column}}\n\n===Points classification===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Points classification (1\u201310)\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Rank\n! scope=\"col\" | Rider\n! scope=\"col\" | Team\n! scope=\"col\" | Points\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Elia Viviani]]|ITA}} {{Cjersey|purple|[[Points classification in the Giro d'Italia|Points classification]]}}\n|{{Ct|QST|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 341\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Sam Bennett (cyclist)|Sam Bennett]]|IRL}}\n|{{Ct|BOH|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 282\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 3\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Davide Ballerini]]|ITA}}\n|{{Ct|ANS|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 147\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Sacha Modolo]]|ITA}}\n|[[EF Education First-Drapac p/b Cannondale|EF Education First\u2013Drapac]]\n| align=\"right\"| 122\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 5\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Simon Yates (cyclist)|Simon Yates]]|GBR}}\n|{{Ct|ORS|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 113\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 6\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Marco Frapporti]]|ITA}}\n|{{Ct|ANS|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 111\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 7\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Danny van Poppel]]|NED}}\n|{{Ct|TLJ|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 107\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 8\n|{{Flagathlete|[[Niccol\u00f2 Bonifazio]]|ITA}}\n|{{Ct|TBM|2018}}\n| align=\"right\"| 9